org.apache.geode.session.tests

Class ContainerManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.geode.session.tests.ContainerManager

  • public class ContainerManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages multiple J2EE containers using cargo. Provides methods to start and stop J2EE containers and obtain the http ports those containers are listening on.
